<doc docid='bbc_war-52578380' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war-52578380' term='COVID'>
Corona Fayras; Maxaa ka jira in dhimasho uusan sababin Corona Fayras ay aad ugu badatay Nigeria?
Dowladda Nigeria ayaa baaritaan ku sameysay caabasho ay shacabka soo gudbiyeen oo ku saabsan dhimasho aad ugu badatay dalkaas, taasoo la sheegayo inuusan sabab u ahayn Corona Fayras.
Dowladda Nigeria ayaa baaritaan ku sameysay caabasho ay shacabka soo gudbiyeen oo ku saabsan dhimasho aad ugu badatay dalkaas, taasoo la sheegayo inuusan sabab u ahayn Corona Fayras.
Arrintan ayaa laga soo tabiyay gobolka ku yaalla waqooyiga dalkaas ee Jigawa.
Dowladda gobolkaas ayaa khubaro caafimaad oo ka kooban shan dhakhtar u dirtay halkaas si ay xog uga soo gudbiyaan ka hor inta uusan dhammaanin isbuucan.
Warbixin ay guddigaas soo saareen maanta ayey ku sheegeen inay wax caddeyn ah u waayeen sare u kac ku yimid tirada dhimashada ee gobolka Jigawa, sidaas awgeedna aysan taageeri karin sheegashada ka timid dhinaca shacabka.
Khubaradan ayaa baaritaan u kuurgalid ah kasoo sameeyay magaalada Hadeja.
Madaxa kooxda baaritaanka sameysay ayaa sheegay in 92 ruux ay ku geeriyoodeen siddeed maalmood gudahood, taasoo qeyrul caadi ah.
Natiijada baaritaanka ayaan meesha looga saarin in dhimashada uu sabab u yahay xanuunka Corona Fayras, maadaama aad dadkaas badankood baaritaan lagu sameynin.
Dadka deegaanka ayaa si weyn uga cawday xaddiga dhimashada oo aad sare ugu kacay xaafadaha qaar.
Dhakhaatiirta ku sugan Jigawa ayaa markii hore sheegay in dadka intooda badan ay halkaas ugu dhintaan xanuunnada kala ah neefta, sokorowga iyo dhiig-karka.
Kooxda baaritaanka loo diray, oo uu ka mid ahaa wakiil ka socda Hay'adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ee WHO ayaa waxay diiradda saarayeen inay ogaadaan waxa keenayay dhimashada iyo inuu Corona Fayras sabab u yahay.
Guddoomiyaha ururka dhakhaatiirta ee Jigawa, Nura Basirka, ayaa sheegay inuu walaac soo food saaray kaddib markii 16 ka mid ah dhakhaatiirta gobolka uu soo ritay Corona Fayras, sidaas darteedna uu dhammaan xubnaha ururka ku amray inay cudurka iska baaraan.
Ilaa hadda gobolkaas waxaa si rasmi ah looga soo tabiyay 39 kiis oo corona ah iyo hal dhimasho oo ka timid xanuunkaas.
Guud ahaan Nigeria waxaa laga helay 3,000 oo kiis, tirada ugu badanna waxaa heysata magaalada Lagos.
Dowladda Nigeria dabcisay xayiraaddii ay kusoo rogtay magaalooyinka waaweyn ee waddanka, taasoo horseedday in dib loo billaabo dhaqdhaqaaqyadii ganacsiga dalka ugu dhaqaalaha badan qaaradda Afrika.
Hase ahaatee ururka dhakhaatiirta ayaa tallaabada dowladda ku qeexay "mid aan laga fiirsanin".
Magaalada ganacsiga hoyga u ah ee Lagos, waxaa laga dareemayaa in saxmadda gaadiidka aysan badneyn, taasoo muujineysa in dad badan ay wali guryaha isku celinayaan.
Isbuucii lasoo dhaafay, madaxweyne Muhammadu Buhari ayaa sheegay in go'aannada xayiraadda ay sababeen "hoos u dhac dhaqaale oo baaxad leh".
Xayiraadda Nigeria ayaa lagu dhawaaqay shan isbuuc ka hor, iyadoo ujeeddadu ahayd si cudurka loo xakameeyo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_war-52061195' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war-52061195' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Shiinaha oo joojinaya ajaaniibta dalkiisa galaya ka dib kiisaskii oo batay
Shiinaha ayaa ku dhawaaqay tallaabo ku meel gaar ah oo lagu mamnuucayo dhammaan ajaanibta booqanaya dalkaas, xitaa haddii ay haystaan dal ku galka ama degganaasha dalkaas.
Shiinaha ayaa ku dhawaaqay tallaabo ku meel gaar ah oo lagu mamnuucayo dhammaan ajaanibta booqanaya dalkaas, xitaa haddii ay haystaan dal ku galka ama degganaasha dalkaas.
Dalkaas ayaa sidoo kale xaddidaya duullimaadyada diyaaradaha Shiinaha iyo kuwa dalalka kale, isagoo ku amray inay toddobaadkii sameeyaan hal duullimaad, iyo in diyaaraduhu aysan buuxin in ka badan 75%.
Inkastoo Shiinaha uu shalay shaaciyay kiiskii ugu horreeyay ee coronavirus ee gudaha dalkaasi, muddo saddex maalmood ah, haddana inta badan dhammaan kiisaska cusub waxay noqdeen kuwo laga qaaday dad dibadda ka yimid.
Waxaa Shiinaha laga soo sheegay shalay 55 kiis oo cusub - kuwaas oo 54 ka mid ah ay bannaanka ka yimaadeen.
Wasaaradda Arrimaha Dibadda Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay inay "joojineyso in ajaanibta ay galaan dalkaas" sababo la xiriira "faafitaanka degdegga ah ee uu Covid-19 ee dunida".
Tallaabadan ayaa saameyneysa dadka haysta dal ku galka iyo deganaashaha dalkaas, balse kuma jiraan diblomaasiyiinta ama dadka haysta dal ku galka badanaa la siiyo shaqaalaha diyaaradaha.
Dadka ka shaqeeya "baahiyaha bani'aadannimo ee degdegga ah" ama kuwa ka shaqeeya howlaha kale ee muhiimka ah ayaa codsan kara in loo oggolaado inay dalkaasi galaan.
Inkastoo shuruucdan ay u muuqdaan kuwo aan la rumeysan karin, haddana shirkado diyaaradeed oo ajnabi ah oo badan ayaa joojiyay inay Shiinaha u duulaan - magaalooyiin badan ayaana dhaqan geliyay tallaabooyinkaas.
Bishii la soo dhaafay, tusaale ahaan, Beijing ayaa ku amartay qof walba oo magaalada ku soo laabanaya inuu galo 14 maalmood oo karantiil ah.
Inkastoo fayraska uu ka soo bilaamay Shiinaha, haddana kiisaska fayraska ee dalkaas waxay ka yar yihiin kuwa Mareykanka, sidoo kale tirada Shiinaha ku dhimatay waxay ka yartahay midda Taliyaaniga iyo Spain.
Kiisaska coronavirus ee Shiinaha waxay gaartay 81,340, iyo 3,292 dhimasho ah, sida uu maanta xaqiijiyay Guddiga Caafimaadka dalkaas.
Guud ahaan, 565 ka mid ah kiisaska la xaqiijiyay ayaa la sheegay in bannaanka laga keenay, oo ay keeneen ajaanib ama muwaadiniinta Shiinaha ee dalkaas ku laabtay.
Hubei - oo ah gobolka uu markii hore ka dillaacay fayraska - lagama soo sheegin kiisas cusub.
Xayiraadda lagu soo rogay caasimadda gobolkaas ee Wuhan, oo dhaqan gashay bishii January, ayaa la sheegay in la khafiifin doono 8 April.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_war-52226514' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war-52226514' term='COVID'>
Magaalada New York oo tiraddii ugu badnayd caalamka uu soo ritay Covid-19
Gobolka New York ayaa noqday gobol ka sara mara dhanka tirada dadka uu soo ritay Corona dalalka kale guud ahaan caalamka marka Mareykanka laga reebo, sida ku cad warbixin la soo saaray.
Gobolka New York ayaa noqday gobol ka sara mara dhanka tirada dadka uu soo ritay Corona dalalka kale guud ahaan caalamka marka Mareykanka laga reebo, sida ku cad warbixin la soo saaray.
Tirada uu magaalada New York soo ritay cudurka Covid-19 ayaa Khamiistii gaartay 159,937, taasi oo ka sara martay dalka Spain oo dadka uu cudurka so ritay ay dhan yihiin (153,000 qof) halka Taliyaaniga ay tiradda gaartay (143,000).
Shiinaha oo ah goobtii uu cudurka ka s bilaabmay ayaa tiradu ahayd 82,000 oo kiis taasi oo micnaheedu tahay in magaalad New York ay ak sara martay dhammaan dalalka klae ee Mareykanka ka baxsan.
Guud ahaan dalka Mareykanka dadka uu cudura soo ritay ayaa tiradoodu gaartay 462,000, halka ay dhimashadu mareyso  ku dhawaad 16,500.
Guud ahaan caalamka tirada uu cudurka soo ritay ayaa imika gaartay 1.6 milyan oo qof, halka tirada dhimashada caalamka ay mareyso 95,000.
Iyada oo magaalada New ay hogaaminayso caalamka tirada dadka uu soo ritay cudurka Corona, dhimashaduna ay taha 7,000 ayaa dhanka dhimashada waxay ka hooseysaa dalka Spain oo ay dhimashadu
mareyso 15,500, halka Taliyaaniga ay cuduka ugu dhinteen 18,000.
Dhanka kale maamulka magaalada New York ayaa waxay bilaabeen inay xabaal wadareedyo ku aasan dadkii u dhintay xanuunka corona, xilli tirada dhimashada ay wali sare u sii kacayso.
Meydadka ayaa lagu aasayaa jasiiradda Hart iyada oo aysan eheladooda ka qeyb galin.
Jasiiradan Hart ayaa lagu aasi jiray dadka ku dhinta magaalada New York ee aan la aqoon eheladooda.
Muuqaalo ay soo duubtay diyaarad ah nooca aan duuliyaha lahayn ayaa muujinaya meydadkaasi oo lagu aasayo xabaal wadareedyo.
Dhanka kale wasiirada dhaqaalaha ee dalalka Yurub ayaa waxay ku heshIiyeen dhaqaala dhan 400 oo bilyan oo Yuuro oo loogu talagalay samatabixinta dalalka Yurub ee sida ba'an uu ugu dhuftay cudurka safmarka ee Corona.
Gudoomiyaha kooxda eurogroup, Mario Centeno, ayaa sheegay in qorshahan uu muhim u yahay xaqiijinta dib u soo kabashada dhaqaalaha si loo difaaco suuqa Yurub.
Lacago deen ah ayaa dalalka Yurub la siin doonaa si ay taasi gacan uga geysato bixinta dhaqaalaha adeega caafimaada iyo si loo caawiyo shirkadaha iyo dadka aan shaqeyn.
