Afar qof oo bukaan ah ayaa tallaalka tijaabada ah lagu siiyay xarunta cilmi-baarista Kaiser Permanente ee Seattle, Washington, sida ay sheegtay wakaaladda wararka ee Associated Press.
Khubarada caafimaadka ayaa sheegay in bilooyin badan ay qaadaneyso xaqiijinta in tallaalkan ama kuwa kale ee laga shaqeynayo ay waxtar leeyihiin.
