UNECA oo ku baaqday dayn cafis
Warbixin ay soo saartay Qaramada Midoobay ayaa waydiisanaysa in ammaah bixiyayaasha caalamiga inay ka cafiyaan amaahda ku leeyihiin saddex waddan oo ay saamaysay Ebola.
