Warbixinta oo ay soo saartay  Hayadda Qaramada Midoobay  ee Gudiga Dhaqaalaha  ee Africa (UNECA), ayaa sheegtay in Sierra Leone, Liberia, iyo Guinea ay fiican tahay inaan ammaah lagu lahayn markii ay cudurka la dagaalamaan.
Waxay sheegtay warbixinta in cudurka uu saamayn ku yeeshay waddamada dhaqaalahooda, gaar ahaan dhinacyada dalxiiska, maalgalinta, adeega bulshada iyo shaqaalaha.
