<doc docid='bbc_140815_ebola_msf_who' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war/2014/08/140815_ebola_msf_who' term='ebola'>
MSF: Ebola lix bil ayaa looga hortagayaa
Hay’adda dhaqaatiirta aan xuduuda lahayn ee MSF ayaa sheegtay in lix bil ay qaadan doonto in xanuunka Ebola la xakameeyo.
Hay’adda dhaqaatiirta aan xuduuda lahayn ee MSF ayaa sheegtay in lix bil ay qaadan doonto in xanuunka Ebola la xakameeyo.
Mar uu weriyayaasha kula hadlaayay magaalada Geneva, madaxada MSF ayaa qeexay in ka hortagidda Ebola ay lamid tahay dagaal hub la isu adeegsanayo. Wuxuuna ku baaqay in maamul wanaag ay la imaadaan shaqaalaha WHO.
Hadalkan ayaa imaanaya saacado kaddib markii WHO ay sheegtay in qiyaasta tirada Ebola inay xad dhaaf noqotay.
MSF ayaa ka digeysa halista bilaabashadii Ebola, iyadoo farta ku fiiqday walwalka tirada la arkay iyo sida uu ugu fiday dhul ballaaran.
Dhowaanahan, hay’adda caafimaadka adduunka ee WHO ayaa si caadi ah uga hadlaysay fididda kiisaska, waxayna sheegtay in Ebola aan la xakameyn karin.
Hadda, in kabadan 1000 qof ayaa u dhintay, MSF ayaa sheegtay in hay’adda ugu wayn dhanka caafimaadka adduunka ee WHO inay waxbadan sameyso si looga hortago Ebola.
Iyadoo dalal badan ay ka qeybgalayaan ka hortagidda Ebola, hadana waxa uu saameyn weyn u geystay ganacsiga iyo hormarada dalalka uu kajiro cudurka.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_141019_eu_ebola' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war/2014/10/141019_eu_ebola' term='ebola'>
Yurub oo ka shireysa faafida Ebola
Wasiiradda arrimaha dibada ee Yurub ayaa maanta ka shiraya sidii ay xoojin lahaayeen jawaabtooda ku aaddan faafida cudurka Ebola.
Wasiiradda arrimaha dibada ee Yurub ayaa maanta ka shiraya sidii ay xoojin lahaayeen jawaabtooda ku aaddan faafida cudurka Ebola.
Dad ay tiradooda ka badan tahay 4,500 oo qof ayaa u dhintay cudurka, waxaana badankood ay ku dhinteen galbeedka Afrika, walow ay jireen dhowr qof oo cudurka ugu dhintay Yurub iyo Mareykanka.
Iyada oo ay sii kordheyso tirada dadka uu cudurka ku dhacayo, ayaa waxa uu Ebola hadda noqday dhibaatada ugu weyn ee soo wajahday wasiiradda arrimaha dibada ee dalalka Yurub.
Waxa ay maanta kulan ku leeyihiin caasimada Luxembourg, iyaga oo dareensan baahida loo qabo in si degdeg ah cudurka loogu xakameeyo Galbeedka Afrika, si aanu ugu faafin dunida inteeda kale.
Guud ahaan dalalka Yurub ayaa ku bixiyay dadaalada lagu xakameynayo cudurka lacag ka badan 400 milyan oo pound.
Ra’iisul wasaaraha UK, David Cameron ayaa doonaya in lacagtaasi la laba-laabo.
Lacagtaasi ayaa ka caawin doonta dalalka Liberia, Sierra Leone iyo Guinea in ay xoojiyaan daryeelkooda caafimaadka, ayna ka gaashaantaan dhibaatada uu cudurka Ebola ku keeni karo dhaqalaahooda.
Balse waxaa xoogeysanaya fikirka ah in loo baahan yahay howlwadeeno caafimaad iyo ciidamo loo diro Galbeedka Afrika, isla markaa gobolkaasi laga dhiso cisbitaalo qalabeysan si cudurka loola dagaallamo.
Ujeedka ayaa ah in la go’doomiyo cudur sidaha, balse aan xiriirka loo jarin dalalka uu saameeyay.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_141019_nigeriaebola' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war/2014/10/141019_nigeriaebola' term='ebola'>
Nigeria oo laga waayey Ebola
In kasta uu cudurka Ebola, uu fara ba'an ku hayo dalalka Sierra Leone, Liberia iyo Guinea, ayaa maanta waxa ay maalin weyn u tahay wadanka Nigeria.
In kasta uu cudurka Ebola, uu fara ba'an ku hayo dalalka Sierra Leone, Liberia iyo Guinea, ayaa maanta waxa ay maalin weyn u tahay wadanka Nigeria.
Hay'ada caafimaadka aduunka ee WHO ayaa maanta lagu wadaa in ay si rasmi ah ugu dhawaaqdo in cudurka Ebola haatan uusan ka jirin dalka Nigeria, oo muddo 6 todobaad ah aanan lagu arkiin kiisaska cudurkaasi.
Bishii July ayaa dalkaasi waxa ka jiray walaac weyn, kaddib markii diblumaasi Liberian ah oo qaba cudurkaasi uu tagay dalkaasi Nigeria.
Dalkaasi ayaa waxaa cudurkan ugu dhintay 8 qof halka kiisaska lagu arkayna ay ahaayeen 20-kiis.
Walaacii laga qabay in cudurkan uu ku faafo dalkan ballaran oo ay ku noolyihiin 170 milyan ee qof ayaa hadda laga hortagay. Balse khubarada caafimaadka ayaa ka digaya in dalka Nigeria uu weli u baahan yahay in uu aad ugu diyaar garoobo haddii uu soo noqdo Ebola, oo ay tahay mid suuragal ah.
Bishii July markii nin Liberian ah oo qabo cudurkaasi uu tagay magaalada Lagos, dalka ma uusan u diyaarsaneyn cudurkaasi, balse iyaga oo kaashanaya gargaar kaga yimi caalamka ayaa waxa ay sameeyeen jawaab celin aad u wanaagsan.
Ku dhawaad 900 oo qof oo suuragal ay aheyd in cudurka ay qaadeen ayaa xaalkooda si dhaw loola socday.
Doctor Stella Ameyo Adadevoh ayaa dalkeeda Nigeria abaal badan u gashay, kaddib markii ay cudurka ka heshay diblumaasigii Liberia u dhashay ayna xaqiijisay in la karantiilo.
Dhakhtaradaasi iyo todoba qof oo kale oo uu ka mid yahay diblumaasiga ayaa Nigeria ugu dhintay cudurka Ebola.
Dadaalka Nigeria ayaa u muuqda mid mira dhalay, balse dagaalka lagula jiro Ebola ee wadankaasi weli ma dhamaan.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_140817_liberia' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war/2014/08/140817_liberia' term='ebola'>
Liberia:Dad weeraray xarun Ebola
Xarun lagu hayay dad looga shakisan yahay inay qabaan cudurka Ebola, ayaa magaalo madaxda Liberia ee Monrovia ayaa dad banaanbaxaya ay weeraraeeen, sida uu boliisku sheegay.
Xarun lagu hayay dad looga shakisan yahay inay qabaan cudurka Ebola, ayaa magaalo madaxda Liberia ee Monrovia ayaa dad banaanbaxaya ay weeraraeeen, sida uu boliisku sheegay.
Arrintan  ayaa ka dhacday meel dad badan ay degan yihiin ee West point Sabtidii habeenimo.
Ugu yaraan labaatan bukaan oo la ilaalinayay inay cudurka qabaan ayaa ka baxsaday xarunta.
Dadka banaanbaxaya ayaan ku faraxsanayn xarunta laga soo raray magaalada dhinayadeeda kale, ayuu sheegay ku xigeenka wasiirka caafimaadka.
Wararka kale ayaa sheegaya inay Ebola tahay been oo ay rabaan inay qasab ku xiraan xarunta.
Xarunta ayaa la furay si loo ilaaliyo bukaanka looga shakisan yahay inay qabo Ebola, kadibna loo gudbiyo xarunta wayn hadii cudurka lagu helo, ayuu BBC u sheegay wasiir ku xigeenka caafimaadka ee Liberia.
Wali lama oga in dadka joogay xarunta ay qabeen Ebola, laakiin wararka qaar ayaa sheegaya inay qabeen cudurka.
</doc>
