Waa dalkii ugu dambeeyay qaaradda Africa ee adkeeya xanibaadda safarka iyadoo ay jirto digniin ka timid hey'adda caafimaadka adduunka ee WHO oo ka digeysay adkeyntan inay sare u qaadeyso cuno yari ka dhacday dalalka uu saameeyay cudurka.
