<doc docid='bbc_141127_ebola_vaccine_trail' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war/2014/11/141127_ebola_vaccine_trail' term='ebola'>
Tijaabadda tallaalka Ebola oo muujiyay natiijo wanaagsan
Khubarada caafimaadka ayaa ammaanay natiijada kasoo baxday tallaal tijaabo ah oo loo sameeyay cudurka Ebola, iyaga oo sheegay in uu noqon karo mid jirka bani'aadamka u sahla in uu aqoonsado oo ka hortago cudur sidaha Ebola.
Khubarada caafimaadka ayaa ammaanay natiijada kasoo baxday tallaal tijaabo ah oo loo sameeyay cudurka Ebola, iyaga oo sheegay in uu noqon karo mid jirka bani'aadamka u sahla in uu aqoonsado oo ka hortago cudur sidaha Ebola.
Labaatan qof oo mutadawiciin ah ayaa tallaalka lagu siiyay dalka Mareykanka, waxaana jirkooda uu yeeshay difaac uu uga hortagi karo cudurka.
Cilmi baarayaasha ayaa sheegaya in natiijada aanay weli cadeyn buuxda u ahayn, in dawada ay waxtar buuxda leedahay, balse la sii wadi doono tijaabada, haddii lagu guuleystana, tallaalka la siin doono kumannaan ah shaqaalaha cafimaadka oo ku sugan galbeedka Afrika, marka la gaaro bisha January.
Dhanka kale shaqaalaha caafimaadka ee cudurka Ebola kula dagaallamaya koonfur bari dalka Guinea, oo ah halka uu cudurka ka bilowday, ayaa BBC-da u sheegay in dhowrkii todobaad ee lasoo dhaafay ay sii kordhayso tirada dadka uu cudurka haleelay.
BBC-da ayaa booqatay mid ka mid ah xarumahaasi cusub oo howl wadeennada caafimaadka ay joojiyeen in ay aqbalaan bukaanno cusub, maadaama ay ka tan bateen kuwii horray ugu jiray.
Xarun kale oo caafimaad ayaa mudo hal todobaad ah waxaa soo gaaray in ka badan boqol qof oo qabta Ebola.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_150609_ebola_un' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.com/somali/war/2015/06/150609_ebola_un' term='ebola'>
Xaruntii Qaramada Midoobay ee Ebola oo la xirayo
Waaxda si dagdag ah uga jawaabida caabuqa ebola oo xaruntoodu ahayd caasimadda Ghana ee Accra ayaa la xirayaa iyada oo Guniea iyo Sierraleaone uu xanuunku ka sii yaranayo.
Waaxda si dagdag ah uga jawaabida caabuqa ebola oo xaruntoodu ahayd caasimadda Ghana ee Accra ayaa la xirayaa iyada oo Guniea iyo Sierraleaone uu xanuunku ka sii yaranayo.
Koox yar ayaa ku hari doonta dalka ilaa dhamaadka bishan June ee sanadkan, kuwaas oo xiriirin doona hawlaha duullimaadyada.
Markii septembartii hore cudurka Ebola uu marayey halkii ugu darnayd Qaramada Midoobay waxay sameeyeen guddi deg deg ah oo gacan ka gaysta jawaabta laga bixinayey cudurka.
Guddiga waxa uu xaruntiisa ka samaystay wadamo ka baxsan kuwii uu ka dilaacay cudurka balse aan wadamadaasi aad uga fogeyn sababtoo ah wadamada uu cudurka ka dilaacay waxa lagu soo rogay xayiraado dhinaca dhaq-dhaqaaqa ah.
Kullan uu la yeeshay madaxweynaha Ghana oo ah kan uu dalkiisa marti-geliyey xarunta gudiga deg deg ah ayaa madaxa Qaramada Midoobay ee gudigaasi Peter Graaff waxa uu sheegay in Ghana ay noqotay wadada keli ah ee loo marayey wadamada Guinea, Liberia iyo Serra leone waxayna taasi suurtagelisay ayuu yiri in kumanaan kun oo qof oo ka jawaab bixinayey Ebola ay halkaasi xarun ka dhigtaan.
Madaxweynaha Ghana John Mahama waxa uu sheegay in xaruntaasi hawsheedii hoos loo dhigay in ay ka turjumayso in guul la gaaray.
Inta badan shaqaalihii iyo qalabkii xaruntaasi ayaa waxa loo wareejiyey dalka Serra leone iyo Guinea, halkaasi oo 24 kiis oo cusub oo Ebola ah laga soo sheegay todobaadkii hore
