Weriyayaasha BBCda oo booqday garoomadaasi, ayaa sheegaya inay arkeen rag ku howlan dhismaha oo isku dayaya in ay hagaajinayaan barxadda garoonka, oo ay dhameystiraan qeybaha kore ee garoonka, sidoo kalana waxa ay rakibayeen albaabada, daaqadaha, musqulaha iyo goobaha lagu qubeysto.
