Ururka ayaa sanadihii lasoo dhaafay si weyn galaangal ugu lahaa siyaasadaha dalalka xubnaha ka ah, waxaana uu goob joogayaal u diray doorashooyin ka dhacayay dalal ka tirsan oo Afrika ku yaalla.
