Mr Kamara oo ka tirsan xisbiga All Peoples Congress (APC) ayaa ka mid ah saddex musharx oo ugu cadcad doorashada.
Musharaxiinta kale ee ugu cadcad waxaa ka mid ah Julius Maada Woni oo ka tirsan Sierra Leone People's Party (SLPP) iyo Kandeh Yumkella oo socda xisbiga National Grand Coalition (NGC).
Mid ka mid ah caqabada ugu wayn ee uu la kulmi doono hogaamiyaha cusub ee la doorto ayaa noqon doonta sidii uu dib ugu dhisi lahaa nidaamka caafimaadka ee dalkaasi ka dib markii sanaddii 2014 uu dalkaasi ka dilaacay cudurka Ebola oo ay ku dhinteen 4,000.
200 oo dhakhtar oo kali ah ayaa ka howlgala dalkaasi oo ay ku nool yihiin 7 milyan oo qof.
Madaxa kormeerayaasha doorashada ee ka socda wadamada barwaaqasooranka madaxwaynihii hore ee Ghana John Mahama, ayaa BBC u sheegay in ay jiraan caddeymo muujinaya in doorashada ay si nabad ah ku dhici doonto.
"Dadka shaqooyiinkooda ayay iska wataan , ma jiro wax walaac iyo cabsi ah oo ay qabaan ". ayuu yiri Mahama.
