Khubarada caafimaadka ayaa hadda doonaya in ay dadka ku tijaabiyaan dawooyinka iyo tallaalka, waxaana dadka iskood u ogolaaday in lagu tijaabiyo ka mid ah shaqaalo caafimaad.
