Dadka Jamhuuriyada Dimoqaraadiga ee Congo ugu dhintay Ebola oo Gaadhay 1,000
Tirada dhimashada ee uu sababay cudurrada Ebola ee Jamhuuriyadda Dimuqraadiga  Congo ayaa gaadhay 1,000, sida ay sheegtay wasaarada caafimaadka.
Tirada dhimashada ee uu sababay cudurrada Ebola ee Jamhuuriyadda Dimuqraadiga  Congo ayaa gaadhay 1,000, sida ay sheegtay wasaarada caafimaadka.
Cudurka wuxuu ka dilaacay DR Congo bishii August, waana kii labaad ee ugu dhimashada badnaa taariikhda.
Agaasime ku xigeenka hay'adda caafimaadka aduunka Dr Michael  Ryan ayaa sheegay in kalsooni darada iyo rabashaduhu ay dhibaato u geysteen,Dedaalada lagu xakameenayo cudurka oo ku sii faafaya barriga dalkaas.
Waxaa la diiwaangeliyay 119 weerar oo lagu qaaday xarumaha caafimaadka iyo howlwadeenadooda ilaa bishii January.
Shaqaalaha caafimaadku waxay haystaan tallaalo fara badan - in ka badan 100,000 oo qof ayaa hore loo siiyey daaweyey.
Balse Rabshadaha joogtada ah ee ka jirta bariga dalka oo ay maleeshiyada joogaan, ayaa sidoo kale uga sii daraya iyadoona aya caqabd ku noqdeen xakameenta Cudurka ayuu yiri Dr Ryan, iyo kalsoonida darrida lagu qabo dhakhaatiirta.
"Waxaan wajaheynaa caqabad weyn oo naga heysta aqbalaada iyo kalsoonida bulshada"DRC waxa kale oo ka dillaacday jadeeco taasi oo dishay in ka badan 1,000 qof, iyadoona laga soo warinayo 50,000 oo kiis.
Shaqaalaha WHO ayaa xaqiijiyay in Jadeecado ay ka jirto 14 ka mid ah 26da gobol ee dalkaasi, miyo iyo magaalo ba.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_141201_ebola_un_targets' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war/2014/12/141201_ebola_un_targets' term='ebola'>
UN ka oo ka digay in Ebola uu dunida ku faafo
Madaxa qaramada midoobey u qaabilsan howlgalka ka hortagga Ebola ee galbeedka Afrika, Tony Banbury, ayaa sheegaya in caabuqan ay weli suura gal tahay inuu ku fido daafaha caalamka.
Madaxa qaramada midoobey u qaabilsan howlgalka ka hortagga Ebola ee galbeedka Afrika, Tony Banbury, ayaa sheegaya in caabuqan ay weli suura gal tahay inuu ku fido daafaha caalamka.
Bishii October ee sanadkan, Mr Banbury ayaa golaha ammaanka ee Qaramada Midoobey u sheegay haddii la doonayo in cudurka si buuxda looga hortago, in ugu dambeyn bishan December, loo baahan yahay in boqolkiiba 70 bukaanada xanuunka qaba ay ku sugnaadaan xarumaha caafimaadka, sdioo kale boqolkiiba 70 dhibanayaasha u dhintay Ebola loo aaso si badqab ah.
Dadka qaba xanuunkan ayaa la sheegayaa inaysan imaan xarumaha lagu daaweeyo taas oo keeneysa in cudurka uu sii fido.
Wareysi uu siiyay BBC-da, oo looga qaaday magaalada caasimadda u ah dalka Sierra Leone ee Freetown, Mr Banbury waxa uu si ku celcelis ah u diiday in la gaaray dhammaan wixii la hiigsanayay.
"Waan ku guuleysanay ama waan dhaafnay bartilmaameedyadaasi meelo badan, waxay u badan tahay in goobo badan aan dhaafnay bartilmaamedkaasi." ayuu yiri asigoo muujinayay in meelaha qaar lagu guuleystay ka hortagidda Ebola.
Balse wuxuu qiray in weli ay jiraan goobo badan oo aan wax badan laga qaban weli, "Balse waxaa jiro meela qaar, oo ay ka mid tahay dalkan Sierra Leone, magaaladan Freetown, iyo Port Loko, oo ah goobaha uu si tirtiib ah hoos ugu dhacayo. Xaqiiqdii waana meelaha aan dooneyno inaan diiradda saarno oo aan ku bixino dhaqaale iyo wixii karaankeena ah,  goobahaasi waa kuwa mudnaanta lasiinayo, waa inaan si adag u shaqeynaa si gargaar loo gaarsiiyo meelahaasi ee aynaa ogeyn inaan gaari doono.”
