UN: Waa wax badan in laga qabto Ebola
Mas'uulka Qaramada Midoobay u qaabilsan la dagaallanka cudurka Ebola, Tony Banbury, ayaa u sheegay BBC in aanu weli haysan awood uu cudurka kaga adkaago.
Mas'uulka Qaramada Midoobay u qaabilsan la dagaallanka cudurka Ebola, Tony Banbury, ayaa u sheegay BBC in aanu weli haysan awood uu cudurka kaga adkaago.
Mr Banbury ayaa hadalkan ka sheegay xarunta Qaramada Midoobay ee la dagaalanka Ebola taasoo ku taalla dalka Ghana oo aanu hadda cudurka soo gaarin, balse deris la ah saddexda dal ee uu cudurka faraha ba'an ku hayo, waa Sierra Leone, Liberia iyo Guinea.
Tony Banbury ayaa mar dhow kasoo laabtay booqasho uu ku tegay saddexda dal ee uu sida ba'an u asiibay cudurka Ebola.
Waxa uu u mahadceliyay dalalka caalamka ee ilaa iyo hadda gacanta ka geystay la tacaallida cudurkan dilaaga ah, balse waxa uu carabka ku adkeeyay in gargaar dheeri ah si degdeg ah loogu baahan yahay.
Tirada dadka ilaa iyo hadda u dhintay cudurka Ebola ayaa kor u dhaaftay 4,800.
Beesha Caalamka ayaa howlgalisay tobannaan kun oo ah shaqaalaha caafimaadka ee dalalka uu cudurka saameeyay, kuwaasi oo maalin waliba khatar ugu jira qaadida cudurka.
Balse tirada dadka u dhimanaya cudurka ayaa sii kordheysa, waxaana uu dhowaan gaaray dalka Mali.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_140528_ebola_west_africa' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/somali/war/2014/05/140528_ebola_west_africa' term='ebola'>
Cudurka Ebola oo gaaray dalal kale
Dad uu saameeyay cudurka dilaaga ah ee Ebola ayaa laga saaray xarun caafimaad, dalka Sierra Leone, ee galbeedka Afrika.
Dad uu saameeyay cudurka dilaaga ah ee Ebola ayaa laga saaray xarun caafimaad, dalka Sierra Leone, ee galbeedka Afrika.
Waxaa jiro cabsi laga qabo inuu fiday cudurka oo markii hore ka dilaacay dalka Guinea, balse hadda uu gaaray dalalka Liberia and Sierra Leone.
Ugu yaraan lix qof ayaa laga saaray cisbitaal ku yaalla bariga dalka Sierra Leone, sida ay sheegayaan saraakiisha wasaaradda caafimaadka oo halkaasi gaaray.
Afar ka mid ah dadkaasi oo la baaray waxaa la ogaaday inay qabaan caabuqa hargabka Ebola, sida ay saraakiisha xaqiijiyeen, Mid ka mid ahaa afartaasi qof ayaa dhintay.
Balse, maamulka may oga halka ay hadda kusugan yihiin dadka kale ee cudurkaasi laga helay, waxayna ka walaacsan yihiin inuu hergabkan uu kufido deegaano hor leh.
Shaqaalaha xarun caafimaadka oo ku taalla magaalada Koindu ee dalka Sierra Leone, meel ku dhow xuduudda Guinea, ayaa isku deyay inay ka hor istaagaan in bukaanadan ay eheladooda ka saaraan cisbitaalka, sida uu sheegay wasiirka caafimaadka.
Balse qaraabada ayaa si adag u dhaqmay si ay ula baxaan dadka laga helay hargabkan Ebola.
Afhayeen u hadlay hay’adda caafimaadka aduunka ee WHO oo ku sugan magaalada Geneva ayaa sheegay in cudurka uu faafay markii xubno qaraabo ah ay isku deyayeen inay daaweeyaan qof uu caabuqa saameeyay oo jirkiisa biyo ka soo bexeen.
Ururka ayaa sheegay in daaweynta laga helayo dhaqaatiirta inay xittaa caawineyso qofka bukaanka ah, balse aysan yareyn karin inuu cudurka fido.
Qiyaastii 200 oo qof ayaa illaa iyo hadda u dhimatay cudurka, dadkaasi badan koodana waxay ku dhinteen dalka Guinea.
Cudurka Ebola waa mid sababa dhimasho degdeg ah, illaa iyo haddana looma hayo dawo looga hortago ama lagu dilo caabuqa uu ka dhasho.
</doc>
