Agaasimaha xarunta xakameynta iyo ka hortagga cudurada, Tom Friedan ayaa Shir jaraa’id ka sheegay in bukaanka laga helay Eboal uu xanuunka ka qaaday dalka Liberia.
Qofka cudurkan halista ah laga helay ma aysan ka muuqan calaamadaha xilligii uu Mareykanka gaarayay.
Dr Friedan waxa uu sheegay inuu aaminsan yahay in kiiskan la xakameyn doono, aysanna ku fideynin gudaha Mareykanka.
