BBC-da ayaa ogaatay in Shirkadda diyaaradaha ee Kenya Airways, ay dib u bilowday duulimaadyadii ay ku tagi jirtay caasimada Sierra Leone ee Freetown.
Waxa ay noqoneysaa diyaaraddii ugu horeysay ee caalami ah ee dib u bilowda duulimaadyada Sierra Leone, xilli cudurka Ebola ee dalkaasi ku dhuftay uu sii wiiqmayo.
