Ebola oo jirka ragga ku jiri karta bilooyin
Daraasaad cusub ayaa sheegaya in nimanka galbeedka Afrika ee ka badbaday Ebola, inay isticmaalaan kondom bilooyin badan si aysan ugu gudbin cudurka markay u tagayaan dumarkooda  bilooyin ka dib.
